# Build artifacts — rebuilt fresh inside the container
**/bin/
**/obj/

# IDE / OS noise
**/.vs/
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Local dev config — NEVER shipped to the container
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Local.json
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Local SQLite DB — mounted via volume, shouldn't be baked into the image
**/data/
**/*.db
**/*.db-journal

# Docs
*.md
LICENSE
